<br>
I'm partial to this server myself, as I wish to Roleplay, but NOT as a Dagger.  The Daggers aren't really a Roleplay guild, I added the RP bit in the forum for those of us who will want to roleplay as well.<br>
<br>
After we get the Dagger thing sorted out, I think a group of us could choose a realm and a day of the week to all play at the same time (Ala Wenesday night in Norrath)<br>
