<br>
The Realm Week suggestion is a way to try to bring us together, without limiting us to a set of class choices that choosing a realm does. However, if it's one of those ideas that ends up separating us even more than we already might be, I'd like to see that in the beginning and nix it. <br>
<br>
We MAY be able to do the Realm of the Week thing, and we may not. At the beginning, I'd like to see us try it out, as we fiddle with server/realm combos as a guild, and if it isn't working and we have to choose a primary realm/server, I think we can. <br>
<br>
